30:14.180 --> 30:18.220
 or reports of what pot does, that's why it does that.

30:18.220 --> 30:20.400
 So you've got these molecules like dopamine

30:20.400 --> 30:22.180
 that make you focused on the things you want

30:22.180 --> 30:23.220
 and the things you crave.

30:23.220 --> 30:24.700
 And then you've got the molecules

30:24.700 --> 30:26.860
