30:36.140 --> 30:38.300
 People that are always in anticipation

30:38.300 --> 30:40.360
 and desire and seeking,

30:40.360 --> 30:42.740
 that's wonderful for pursuing goals.

30:42.740 --> 30:45.180
 However, it's terrible for enjoying life.

30:45.180 --> 30:46.000
 And actually those people

