31:03.740 --> 31:05.540
 they can be very manipulative.

31:05.540 --> 31:07.820
 Dopamine and the pursuit of something

31:07.820 --> 31:10.080
 doesn't necessarily have to be high energy

31:10.080 --> 31:12.180
 and intense from the outside

31:12.180 --> 31:13.640
 when you observe it from the outside.

