 which is 99.9% L-DOPA, the precursor to dopamine.

36:28.080 --> 36:31.060
 So there are people that do much better

36:31.060 --> 36:34.820
 when they take things that increase their dopamine levels.

36:34.820 --> 36:39.020
 There are antidepressants like wellbutrin, bupryron

36:39.020 --> 36:41.240
